⚠️ DATA USAGE & LIABILITY DISCLAIMER

1. UNOFFICIAL API USAGE
   This software ('Sentinel') utilizes the 'yfinance' library to fetch market 
   data. 'yfinance' is an unofficial library that scrapes data from Yahoo 
   Finance. This method is subject to rate limiting, potential service 
   interruptions, and changes to Yahoo's data structure. The authors of 
   Sentinel have no control over the availability or accuracy of this data.

2. TERMS OF SERVICE COMPLIANCE
   You (the User) are solely responsible for ensuring your use of the data 
   retrieved by this software complies with Yahoo Finance's Terms of Service 
   and acceptable use policies. If you intend to use this software for 
   commercial, institutional, or high-frequency automated purposes, you 
   should implement a licensed data provider (e.g., Polygon.io, IBKR) as 
   discussed in the software documentation.

⚠️ FINANCIAL DISCLAIMER

This software is for educational, research, and informational purposes only. 
Nothing in this software constitutes financial, investment, or trading advice. 
The option pricing models (Bjerksund-Stensland) and volatility forecasts 
(GARCH) included in this tool are theoretical approximations and do not 
guarantee future market behavior. 

Trade at your own risk. The author (Omar Alaaeldein) is not liable for any 
financial losses incurred through the use of this software.